				<td colspan="2"><span>Im very much thinking about leaving my current guild, not too happy with the rate at things are moving, summer vacation is coming up and im going to the states for 3 months. The wonders of this is I'm going to be able to attend raids without it being 3 AM <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" />. Im most likely going to be joing a DKP guild, my question to you is What do I do on raids depending on where I am, Healer group is easy (feed mana), but the MT group and the DPS groups are kinda tricky. Im definately gonna be 65 by the time I'm back in the good Ole' U.S of A, but just getting ontop of my game. Much help appreciated.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
(OOT BTW CELEADOR ZEPPELIN OWNS!!!!!!!!)</span></td>
