				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Pre-Elemental and Elemental Bards<a name="41712"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 24 04 10:44 AM</span></td>
