				<td colspan="2"><span>If you're raiding on the pre-elemental tier -- Tier 3 gods and elemental bosses -- then this is my recommendation:
<br />

<br />
For main tank: Niv's Harmonic (AC), Psalm of Veeshan (resists+DS+AC), and Solon's Charismatic Concord (Charisma).
<br />

<br />
For melee DPS: Warsong of Zek, Call of the Muse, and might as well throw in Marr for the regen and any mana needs.
<br />

<br />
For caster DPS: Call of the Muse, Marr, and probably resists if there is AE to contend with.  If not, thrown in a Chant or HOS to set the table for your casters -- find out what resists they want debuffed most.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
